Title: Worakls
Description: Worakls, the maestro of melodies, continues to redefine electronic music. His innate musicality, honed through years of classical training, seamlessly blends with his passion for electronic sounds. The result is a captivating sonic tapestry woven from powerful orchestrations, driving rhythms, and dreamy melodies. Each track is a journey, an exploration of emotions that resonates deeply with listeners, showcasing the true artistry that lies at the heart of Worakls' music.

Title: Aaron Hibell
Description: Aaron Hibell is the dynamic young producer bridging the gap between the symphony hall and the dance floor. After dropping university for his craft, the English native cemented his place in the UK scene by producing for Europe’s elite. Inspired by classical music, Hibell crafts captivating electronic sounds that effortlessly blend techno, trance, and house with orchestral elements, pushing both cinematic and electronic boundaries.

Title: Polyamor
Description: polyamor is a Berlin-based record label that embodies a spirit of musical exploration and artistic freedom. They champion a diverse roster of artists who push boundaries and defy genre conventions, creating a sound that is as eclectic as it is exciting. But polyamor is more than just a label, it's an experience.
